{"word":"ἐπιφύω","slug":"ἐπιφύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιφύω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ύσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to produce on</i> or <i>besides</i>, <b><a href='S:Theophrastus'>Theophr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, with aor2 and <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>ἐπέφῡν, ἐπιπέφῡκα</el>, <i>to grow upon</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:— of dogs, <i>to stick close to</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to be born after</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}